{
  "stem": "210.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So my husband would write-- and, you know, and make like a post office, you know, to write back.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he would write back and tell them, whoever you are, please come.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I am-- I'll be only too happy to let you watch and teach you.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's not something that I can give you a recipe, like for a cake.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anyway, this went on for months.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in the meantime, mine-- my husband's cousin, you know, he knew everything what's going on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they started, you know-- they gave my husband a gun.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He went around with a gun.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Every time we went out, he was with a gun.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I got sick and tired.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, you know, we lived on the second floor.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I got sick and tired of living like this-- being scared.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Whenever we went into the building, we looked on all sides if there was somebody not waiting to kill my husband.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he went around with a gun.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I told him, the same thing-- that I didn't want to be in Opoczno.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't want to live this way either.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we are gonna leave.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So my-- my-- you know, my friends-- so when we told them we're gonna leave-- so they wouldn't wanna-- didn't want us to leave.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And by that time, the Russians, you know, sent, let's say, people to stay overnight with us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we would be in the-- asleep in the bedroom, and they would sit outside with a bottle of vodka and drink a whole night.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In the morning, he would leave.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said, I cannot live like this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I don't want to live like this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we want to leave.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
